{
  "stem": "10549.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the first time that I came to a camp where they gave me my own bunk to sleep on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took us every morning, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] walking maybe three, four miles to woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was cold and snowy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had wooden shoes on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Wooden shoes-- the shoes were with a wooden sole-- sole-- I mean, a leather top, but a wooden sole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we were walking through the snow, the snow used to stick-- get stuck to the wooden sole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were walking like on stilts because the snow was-- so we had to stop every little while and knock off the snow from the shoes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the walking wasn't as bad as knocking off each time there was heavy, because the snow, the shoes were heavy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was like a torture almost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were walking for-- for over two weeks, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had to go every morning to the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything was frozen and cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they gave us a-- a-- a pick and shovel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had to dig out old tree stumps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everything was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So actually didn't have no-- the reason-- there was no reason for digging up those stumps because those were frozen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it seems like they-- they just wanted to punish us or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After two weeks in that labor thing I was going through, they picked me to a factory, which were making parts-- airplane parts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was a great thing for me because I didn't have to be on the outsides in the woods.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was making airplane parts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was an assembly line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in that assembly line, we were making airplane parts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Condition were not great.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
